data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home, boasting over 4000 sqft. of luxurious living space sprawling over a 3/4 acre wooded lot. This meticulously maintained and updated residence offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. This home features two master bedrooms, each with its own en suite. With the potential for up to six bedrooms, this residence offers versatile living spaces to suit your needs. The heart of this home lies in its large eat-in kitchen, adorned with Corian custom counters and sink and custom cabinetry. There is a commercial exhaust over the built-in grill system and a walk-in pantry makes this kitchen a chef's dream. The family room has a gas fireplace, attached sitting room, and a convenient wet bar, creating cozy ambiance for gatherings. The hardwood floors throughout add a touch of sophistication, while the bathrooms, 3 full and 1 half showcase quartz, marble, and Corian vanity counters. The sunroom with Pella floor-to-ceiling windows & radiant heated floor, provides a serene space to enjoy nature's surroundings. This home also includes a bonus room on the first floor and another on the second floor.  Either could be a yoga room, large home office, additional bedroom, many possibilities.  The finished basement features nature stone flooring in the rec room plus, additional storage. This home has a horseshoe driveway leading to an oversized finished garage. Updates and improvements abound in the home, including a 2022 AC system, 2017 furnace, 2020 asphalt roof, vinyl siding, gutters, and more. Don't miss the chance to own this extraordinary home, where every detail is thoughtfully considered for luxurious and comfortable living. If all of this wasn't enough, this home is located in a highly desired neighborhood on a dead-end street.  You can even walk to the park for soccer practice, tennis courts, playground and a beautiful walking path.  Schedule your private showing today and make this dream home YOUR reality.
